node.text:
ASMR unpacking of new iPad Pro + Apple Pencil😴

I didn't want to buy a new iPad for a long time, but my old one started to fail, it was inconvenient to draw, so I began to draw less often.  Now I feel comfortable and I want to create more!

Painting done in Procreate app 
Brushes: Bluesssatan brush set, Comfy brush set, Easy makeup brush set (link in my bio)
